      <section class="- topic/section " id="processing-expectations" xtrc="section:1;16:45" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/keyword.dita">
         <title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:2;17:17" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/keyword.dita">Processing expectations</title>
         <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:1;18:13" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/keyword.dita">When used within the <xmlelement class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlelement " xtrc="xmlelement:3;18:46" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/keyword.dita">keywords</xmlelement> element, the content of a
               <xmlelement class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlelement " xtrc="xmlelement:4;19:28" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/keyword.dita">keyword</xmlelement> element is considered to be metadata and should be
            processed as appropriate for the given output medium.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:2;21:13" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/keyword.dita">Elements that are specialized from the <xmlelement class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlelement " xtrc="xmlelement:5;21:64" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/keyword.dita">keyword</xmlelement>element might
            have extended processing, such as specific formatting or automatic indexing. </p>
      </section>
